<h3 id="kyle-maclachlan-as-thomas-edison">Kyle MacLachlan <em>as</em> Thomas Edison</h3>

<p><img src="\assets\images\edison.jpg" class="cast" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Film Antagonist</li>
  <li>Operated <strong>Edison Machine Works</strong>, where he and hired scientists (including Tesla for some time) tested and manufactured electrical devices</li>
  <li>Patented direct current technology for use in early electrical grids</li>
  <li>Provoked ‚ÄúThe War of the Currents‚Äù to maintain DIRECT CURRENT supremacy while ALTERNATING CURRENT technologies proved more efficient and effective at carrying electrical voltage across distance.</li>
  <li>Link: <a href="https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001492/">IMDb Record</a> for Kyle MacLachlan</li>
</ul>

